com.github.arachnidium.model.support.annotations

Annotation Type DefaultPageIndex


  • @Target(value={TYPE,FIELD})
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface DefaultPageIndex
    This annotation is for UI specifications when it is possible the interaction with more than one browser window at the same time. If some page is always loaded at the first window (or second and so on) the class-specification could be marked by the annotation.

    Examples:

    @DefaultPageIndex(index = 0) //is always on the first browser window

    public class ...

    or

    @DefaultPageIndex(index = 1) //is always on the second browser window

    public class ...

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      int index 

    • Element Detail

      • index

        public abstract int index
        Returns:
        The specified default browser window index
